\c 9
\s Jehovha anozviratidzazve kuna Soromoni
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika pakupedza kwaSoromoni kuvaka imba yaJehovha neimba yamambo nechishuwo chese chaSoromoni chaaifarira kuita,
\v 2 kuti Jehovha wakaonekwa kuna Soromoni rwechipiri sezvaaiva aonekwa kwaari paGibhiyoni.
\v 3 Jehovha ndokuti kwaari: Ndanzwa munyengetero wako nemukumbiro wako zvawandiitira, ndaita imba ino tsvene yawakavaka kuisa zita rangupo rinhi narinhi uyr meso angu nemoyo wangu zvichavapo mazuva ese.
\v 4 Kana uriwe, kana uchifamba pamberi pangu saDhavhidhi baba vako nemoyo unorevesa, nekururama, kuita zvese zvandakakuraira, kuchengeta vimiso zvangu nemitongo yangu,
\v 5 ipapo ndichasimbisa chigaro chako cheushe pamusoro paIsraeri rinhi narinhi sezvandakavimbisa Dhavhidhi baba vako, ndichiti: Hakungashaikwi munhu achagara pachigaro cheushe chaIsraeri.
\v 6 Kana mukatendeuka zvekutendeuka imwi nevana venyu uye mukasachengeta mirairo yangu, zvimiso zvandakaisa pamberi penyu, asi mukaenda mukashumira vamwe vamwari ndokuvanamata;
\v 7 ipapo ndichagura Israeri kubva panyika yandakavapa; neimba iyi yandakaitira tsvene zita rangu, ndichairasira kure nechiso changu uye Israeri achava shumo nechiseko pakati pevanhu vese;
\v 8 uye imba iyi yakakwirira, wese aanopfuura nayo achashamiswa uye acharidza muridzo, uye vachati: Jehovha wakaitirei kudai kunyika ino uye kuimba ino?
\v 9 Zvino vachiti: Nokuti vakasiya Jehovha Mwari wavo, wakabudisa madzibaba avo munyika yeEgipita, ndokubatirira vamwe vamwari ndokuvashumira, ndokuvabatira naizvozvo Jehovha wavaburusira chakaipa chose ichi.
\s Maguta akavakwa naSoromoni
\p
\v 10 Zvino zvakaitika pakupera kwemakore makumi maviri Soromoni avaka dzimba idzi mbiri, imba yaJehovha neimba yamambo;
\v 11 (zvino Hiramu mambo weTire waiva atsigira Soromoni nematanda emisidhari; uye nematanda emisipiresi, uye negoridhe, zvichienderana nechishuwo chake chese) nenguva iyo mambo Soromoni wakapa Hiramu maguta makumi maviri panyika yeGarirea.
\v 12 Hiramu ndokubuda akabva Tire kuzoona maguta Soromoni aaiva amupa, asi aiva asina kunaka pameso ake.
\v 13 Ndokuti: Magutai awa awandipa, hama yangu? Zvino wakaatumidza nyika yeKabhuri kusvika nhasi.
\v 14 Zvino Hiramu wakatumira mambo matarenda egoridhe zana nemakumi maviri.
\p
\v 15 Zvino ndiro shoko rechibharo chakarairwa namambo Soromoni, kuzovaka imba yaJehovha, neimba yake, neMiro, norusvingo rweJerusarema, neHazori, neMegidho, neGezeri.
\v 16 Farao mambo weEgipita wakange anokunda Gezeri, akaripisa nomoto, akauraya VaKenani vakange vagere muguta, akaripa mukunda wake, mukadzi waSoromoni.
\v 17 Soromoni akavaka Gezeri, neBhe- tihoroni rezasi,
\v 18 naBharati, neTamari, murenje munyika iyo,
\v 19 namaguta ese amatura aSoromoni, namaguta engoro dzake, namaguta avatasvi vamabhiza ake, nezvese Soromoni zvaaida kuzvivakira paJerusarema, napaRebhanoni, napanyika yese yakange yakabatwa naye.
\v 20 Kuvanhu vese vakange vasara vaVaAmori, naVaHiti, naVaPerezi, naVaHivhi naVaJebhusi, vakange vasi vana vaIsraeri;
\v 21 navana vavo vakange vasara panyika shure kwavo, ivo vana vaIsraeri vakange vasingagoni kuvaparadza chose kuna ivavo Soromoni wakaraira chibharo chavaranda kusvikira nhasi.
\v 22 Asi Soromoni haana kuita varanda pakati pavana vaIsraeri, asi ivo vaiva varwi vake, navabatiri vake, namachinda ake, navakuru vake, navarairi vengoro dzake, navatasvi vamabhiza ake.
\v 23 Ndivo vaiva vatariri vakuru vamabasa aSoromoni, vaiva namazana mashanu namakumi mashanu, vairairira vanhu vaibata basa.
\p
\v 24 Zvino mukunda waFarao wakabva kuguta raDhavhidhi, akaenda kuimba yake, yaakange avakirwa naSoromoni; ipapo akavaka Miro.
\p
\v 25 Katatu pagore Soromoni waibaira zvipiriso zvinopiswa nezvipiriso zvokuyananisa pamusoro pearitari yaakange avakira Jehovha, akapisa zvinonhuhwira pamwe chete nazvo paaritari yakange iri pamberi paJehovha. Naizvozvo akapedza imba.
\p
\v 26 Mambo Soromoni wakavakawo zvikepe zvizhinji paEZiyonigebheri, pedo neEroti, pamahombekombe eGungwa Dzvuku, panyika yaEdhomu.
\v 27 Hiramu akatuma nezvikepe izvo varanda vake, vaiva vafambisi vezvikepe vaiziva gungwa kwazvo, pamwe chete navaranda vaSoromoni.
\v 28 Vakasvika Ofiri, vakatorapo goridhe rakasvika matarenda ana mazana mana namakumi maviri vakauya nayo kuna mambo Soromoni.